"rather a symbolic link to another target like <systemitem>graphic.target</"
"systemitem>. Can be permanently changed via &yast; (see <xref linkend=\"sec."
"boot.runlevel.edit\"/>). To change it for a session, use the Kernel command "
"line option <literal>systemd.unit=<replaceable>&lt;my_target&gt;.target</"
"replaceable></literal> at the boot prompt."
msgstr ""

