#. Tag: para
#: systemd.xml:1321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starting or stopping a service changes its status for the currently running "
"session. To change its status throughout a reboot, you need to enable or "
"disable it."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: systemd.xml:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enabling or Disabling a Service"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: systemd.xml:1331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
